datacube.search.share.impl

Class SearchArray

  • java.lang.Object
    • datacube.search.share.impl.SearchArray

  • public class SearchArray
extends java.lang.Object
    This class implements search functions and methods to separate and collect 2D arrays from 3D arrays
    Some search functions refers to http://www.kosbie.net/cmu/fall-08/15-100/handouts/notes-two-dimensional-arrays.html#deepToString
    Author:
    btdiem
